9B%25A4%25EF%25BD%259C4%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2589%258D%25E6%258E%25A5%25E7%2581%25AB%25E6%25A3%2592%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%259B%25A4%25E5%25BE%258C%25E6%2596%25B7%25E4%25BE%259B%2520%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%25973%25E6%2588%25BF%25E8%25BF%2591-1217%25E8%2590%25AC%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E5%2585%25A5%2520%25E4%25BB%258A-720%25E8%2590%25AC6%25E6%258A%2598%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E6%25A8%2593%3Fmtc%3D60037&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=07a90f90922023dbaba062939a0cb07e&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank" uhash="07a90f90922023dbaba062939a0cb07e"&gt;銀主盤撈筍盤｜4年前接火棒買新盤後斷供 元朗3房近$1217萬買入 今$720萬6折賣樓&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32095294&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=102340950969295f2f887f41_97974703"/><published>2025-11-28T14:38:48+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>f105aae3db2bd8edb049046d42068463</id><title>宏福苑：一個史詩式的災難。</title><updated>2025-11-28T14:40:27+08:00</updated><author><name>倒吊滴水</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-11-28T14:40:27+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_574841677"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_574841677"&gt;緣起:&lt;br&gt;工程用人不當，監管無力，無力係指縱是污煙瘴氣，路人皆見，最終以歷史悲劇結尾。正是天地不仁，以萬物為芻狗。芻狗者祭祀之物也，人不過是天地過客，無法改寫厄運？&lt;br/&gt;其實老子講天地不仁，係指上蒼無心於萬物，一視同仁，人世間一齊網紀法則，不為個別行為所影響，佛家說共業者，近矣。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;後續:&lt;br/&gt;近二千戶近乎灰飛煙滅。原地重建是最佳解決方法。長江李氏掌門人近百歲，最後可以為大埔灑下甘露，觀音腳下留淚痕。&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32095295&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=102340950969295f2f887f41_97974703"/><published>2025-11-28T14:40:27+08:00</published></entry><entry